step_description: Are you importing the good for any of the following purposes? trade samples, laboratory samples or as display items for exhibitions, which are not intended to be placed on the market; consignments of food and feed which form part of passengers personal luggage and are intended for personal consumption or use; non-commercial consignments of food and feed sent to natural persons which are not intended to be placed on the market; consignments of food and feed intended for scientific purposes.
